Scheduler 0.0.0
=======

plugin/gem for easy scheduling recurring tasks for ruby projects

Example
=======

Scheduler::Cron::Configuration.configure do |cron|
  cron.run('do:some:stuff').daily.at_hour(1).at_minute(1)
  cron.run('do:more:stuff').on_day_of_week(:mon, :wed).at_hour(5).at_minute(1)
end


